{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "第十二回\"一剑穿心\"。驼队中连续发生离奇命案，孙亮被自己的蛇鞭绞死，冯浩被自己的金背刀斩首，一夜之间又有两人死亡。小方与波娃在帐篷中互诉衷肠，波娃透露操控她的\"唯一\"是她的姐姐，小方发誓保护她。驼队首领唐麟召集众人分析案情，认定凶手是队伍内部之人，目标是驼队货物。驼子指出货物已被割开查验。唐麟怀疑小方是唯一来历不明之人，令其不得离开帐篷。加答挺身为小方辩护，但被唐麟反驳。会后唐麟在帐篷中被一剑穿心杀死，凶手仍是谜。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_wa",
      "speaker_name": "波娃",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "她是我的姐姐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bo_wa",
      "listener_name": "波娃",
      "text": "谁是你的姐姐？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bo_wa",
      "listener_name": "波娃",
      "text": "你从来不反抗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_wa",
      "speaker_name": "波娃",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "我从来没有想到过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bo_wa",
      "listener_name": "波娃",
      "text": "从今以后，只要我活着，就绝不会让你再被人欺侮。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_wa",
      "speaker_name": "波娃",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "你现在虽然这么说，可是将来呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_wa",
      "speaker_name": "波娃",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "谁知道将来会发生什么事？说不定你也会变的。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bo_wa",
      "listener_name": "波娃",
      "text": "不管将来发生什么事，我都不会变，你一定要相信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_wa",
      "speaker_name": "波娃",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "我相信。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "我们已分批出去搜查过，附近三十里之内，绝无人迹。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "所以杀死孙亮他们的凶手，必定就是我们这队伍里的人，现在一定还留在队伍里。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "这队伍中能杀死他们五个人的并不多。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_tang_lin",
      "listener_name": "唐麟",
      "text": "五个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "是五个人。你睡觉的时候，又死了两个，你一定睡得很熟，所以连他们死前的惨呼都没有听见。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "他们五个人的来历不同，武功门户也不同，更没有同时与人结仇，所以他们的死，绝对不是仇杀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "他们被杀，一定是因为有人想动我们这批货。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": "char_tang_lin",
      "listener_name": "唐麟",
      "text": "货物已经被人动过，而且有十几包货都已被人割开，想必是因为那个人先要看看这些货是不是值得他动手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": "char_tuo_zi",
      "listener_name": "驼子",
      "text": "如果是你，你认为是否值得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": "char_tang_lin",
      "listener_name": "唐麟",
      "text": "绝对值得。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "这批货一个人虽然搬不走，但是他如果能将我们一个个全都暗杀，货就是他的了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "现在我们虽然还不知道这个人是谁，但是我们一定能查出来，因为这队伍中每个人的来历我们都已调查得清楚。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "在凶手还未查出之前，我们暂时留在此处，谁也不准离开队伍。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "尤其是你，你暂时最好不要离开你的帐篷一步。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "你最好现在就回到你的帐篷里去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da",
      "speaker_name": "加答",
      "listener": "char_tang_lin",
      "listener_name": "唐麟",
      "text": "不是他，他不是。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": "char_jia_da",
      "listener_name": "加答",
      "text": "不是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da",
      "speaker_name": "加答",
      "listener": "char_tang_lin",
      "listener_name": "唐麟",
      "text": "不是你们说的那个人，我不是瞎子，他杀了人，我看得见。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": "char_jia_da",
      "listener_name": "加答",
      "text": "你看得见？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da",
      "speaker_name": "加答",
      "listener": "char_tang_lin",
      "listener_name": "唐麟",
      "text": "我跟他，他跟我，就好像一个人跟一个人的影子，一直在一起。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": "char_jia_da",
      "listener_name": "加答",
      "text": "你抱着马沙的尸体痛哭流涕时，你也看见他在那里？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "我的话已经说完了，我的意思你们一定完全都明白。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "你们走吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    }
  ],
